main event: A large, dark object was observed passing rapidly overhead near Bakersfield, California on May 13, 1952 at 2:56 PM.
interesting points: The object was observed by multiple witnesses, including the Kern County Sheriff's Office.
The object was described as large and dark, passing rapidly overhead.
The sighting occurred at 2:56 PM on May 13, 1952.
The report was received by telephone from Bakersfield, California.
The report was forwarded to various military and intelligence agencies for further investigation.
witnesses: Kern County Sheriff's Office, multiple witnesses
